latestPosts.caption:
Backbends with yoga wheel @wiselife.in 💛

I love working on backbends and adding props is a great way to assist me in those beautiful arches. 

So many ways to get creative and use the yoga wheel to open up the entire length of your spine. 

🔆 Extended puppy pose with wheel helps with deeper thoracic opening 

🔆 Spinal Massage- feels as good as it sounds, a great way to warm up the spine before trying any advanced backbends. A beginner friendly movement that can be practiced as per ones flexibility 

🔆 flowing into elbow chakrasana while gripping the edges of the wheel helps with locking the elbows for a deeper thoracic opening. 
Extend your knees for a more advanced setubandh chakrasana vinyasa 

🔆 Kapotasana can also be assisted for those who are still working on controlling the  drop back 

🔆 And finally for Shalabhasana, the yoga wheel is a great prop to take the weight off the chin helping you ease into the locust pose 

Give these a try if you’re looking to improve your backbends slowly! 

#yogaflow #yogaprops #yoga #backbending  #yogawheel #yogateacher #yogahowto #yogawheel #wiselife

Waking up to the sounds of nature and flowing through yoga at Sohum, Arambol was truly therapeutic. 

Surrounded by calming energy and positive vibes, every morning felt like a reset—for the body, mind, and soul. 

The peaceful setting helped us reconnect with ourselves in the most beautiful way.

So grateful this soulful corner of the world brought me back to my mat, back to stillness, and back to me.

Thanks to @azury_wellness @muktika_wellness @yogawithvaibhavi for curating this 🌸
